{"tid":1301894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣彈藥長文] 香港警察高薪待遇好，因為法律規定不可參與政治！","createTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T16:13:50.000Z","uid":262662,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f6534e135ee84418fc7b21e77cf146ff0ea9f3","tid":1301894,"uid":262662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"譚文豪尋日講過差佬幾個協會不斷出聲鬧醫護人員、法律人員、議員甚至英國議員係完全違反《警隊條例》要求既政治中立，可以廢除獨立薪級表。好多人都唔明差佬點解紀律部隊中咁高人工，其實除左因為危險（消防唔危險咩？），仲因為有嚴格政治中立要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/121829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F121829&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=11290ecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/121829</a><br />\n（作者Joe Yeung，文好長好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 節錄如下）<br />\n<br />\n//因為要豁免《警隊條例》中禁止參加職工會的限制，三個協會己獲得處長所承認，地位超然。可是員佐級協會當時仍屬法外之物，職級又不及前三者，所以修例就是要讓員佐級協會正名，將<span style=\"color: red;\">怨氣納入體制之中解決，亦透過升格與「大Sir」們睇齊，從而安撫情緒，收買人心</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n//香港警察隊員佐級協會就成為了高層與低級警員作溝通用的「既有渠道」，以溝通渠道換取警員守法，同時防止警員用任何方式向外洩憤，藉此確立警隊的紀律及專業操守的形象。而<span style=\"color: red;\">因為發生過警員圍攻廉署的失控暴力事件</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，員佐級協會的存在更是歷史上的一道明鏡，時刻提點警員任何原因都不是犯法的藉口，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">無論如何都不能用言語或行為對外發洩，協會的存在實在別具意義</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n//警員亦應明白，加入職工會並非毫無限制，他們只能對向內表達意見，亦只能討論<span style=\"color: red;\">薪酬待遇及福利事宜</span>，藉以保持政治中立及專業穩定的行為及形像。這是白紙黑字的立法原意，無可爭辯。<br />\n<br />\n政府一直保留這個限制，甚至於後來的薪酬檢討中亦可見一斑。1988年，政府繼續改革公務員薪酬待遇的制度，成立了「凌衞理委員會」，專門檢視紀律部隊的薪酬調整機制。<br />\n<br />\n當年重點之一，是警隊要求成立獨立的薪級表，<span style=\"color: red;\">使之與消防、海關、入境及懲教的薪酬調整機制拆開</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。當時《凌衞理報告書》回應了警隊的要求，時至今日，警隊的薪級仍是各隊之中最豐厚的一隊。而《凌衞理報告書》亦將消防隊伍由緊急紀律部隊降格為一般紀律部隊，更將警隊定性為「最終執法機關」（the agency of last resort）。如此一抬一踩地誇獎警隊，政府在警隊心理需求上實在是氹到盡，警隊理應知足及安份守己。//<br />\n<br />\n//給予警隊的豐厚薪酬及獨有超然地位，是因為《凌衞理報告書》充分考慮了警隊的工作性質（內有多段討論，有興趣可以詳讀），因而作出金錢上及心理上補償，確確實實是&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">they are well paid for it</span>&rdquo;。《凌衞理報告書》第8.44段明確寫出贊成警察擁有獨立薪酬機制的關鍵理據，主要是因為法例<span style=\"color: red;\">禁止警察參加工會、禁止擅離職守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及要求保持政治中立</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n文宣巴打請睇睇有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac611af710bf3e69f6b1f512b1a5a88b2401381","tid":1301894,"uid":262662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"b8370466b8719da779058f6a33f42bb82d67fbfc","tid":1301894,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>TVB港姐</ins> - <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1300556\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1300556</a><br />\n<strong>7.10</strong> - <ins>麥小姐追思會</ins> ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場 - 19:00~22:30<br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>梁烈士公眾告別禮</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=8613b443\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n<strong>7.11</strong> - <ins>油尖旺區議會夢遊</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=462b0f42\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/ytm_dc711</a><br />\n<strong>7.12</strong> - <ins>光復港大 守衛我城</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2S6Lw1T&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=83362710\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2S6Lw1T</a><br />\n<strong>7.13</strong> - <ins>光復上水</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/32eEvRm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32eEvRm&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=26769791\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/32eEvRm</a><br />\n<strong>7.14</strong> - <ins>沙田區大遊行</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/st7142019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fst7142019&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=746472ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/st7142019</a><br />\n<strong>7.28</strong> - <ins>將軍澳遊行</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/tko728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko728&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=c7f4e445\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/tko728</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>抵制TVB</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=b0da52c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>美國聯署 人權民主法案</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=66ed174a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n</span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>撤回修例 收回暴動 撤銷控罪 追究警隊 雙真普選<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化</em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有信用評分之後 痴memo 遊行 上網講錯嘢 信錯教都可能扣你分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請不要再裝睡 行動吧香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得簽聯署呀!!!香港人權和民主法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=09ec2d0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBAj6Qv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBAj6Qv.gif&h=8056e3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOJO3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOJO3Q.gif&h=92e11c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOtUVJR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOtUVJR.gif&h=eaa393bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLA4yvw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLA4yvw.gif&h=3a86806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFOqhXb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFOqhXb.gif&h=b24b8c4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33df3ec6a463443e8c68f367db8875f81878021b","tid":1301894,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea32cd7cba4719d6e8b30531beeb6f1031c5c60b","tid":1301894,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:20:25.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e35c08df5e60d2e2740228bdaa5ceceba45fdf1","tid":1301894,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"歡迎入內討論<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3602088df56a710e0052778396f944f7a457441d","tid":1301894,"uid":277519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc85509f59f0728b53b319dceb79495c252ed0b4","tid":1301894,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc6e72a64cd09432d319439b1fbef6f60b3af26","tid":1301894,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"c58c8f53459874942c7522d50f3662b714d03783","tid":1301894,"uid":60539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:25:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"42cffcf43b35185e6d28f0f0e85185bbbdc9b2e3","tid":1301894,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:26:40.000Z","msg":"文宣方面<br />\n首先要解釋下咩叫政治中立先<br />\n<br />\n就咁講警察違反政治中立唔係人人都明"},{"pid":"ce1f9cbeec80da733ee97f90c1b9c84f9bf4e8ab","tid":1301894,"uid":116734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"游行無人提無人推<br />\n光複上水集合地點換左北區運動場籃球場<br />\n有無人知？<br />\n開左tg group幫手搞口號 揾緊義工有無人知？<br />\n個個爭住講memo tvb<br />\n<br />\n我地游行要向政府 施壓 要求回應我哋五大訴求  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 是為主菜</span><br />\n<br />\n搞9 tvb同用memo紙 作另類文宣 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">是為配菜</span><br />\n<br />\ne+ 淨係搞tvb同memo紙大圍已經失焦 步緊雨傘後塵"},{"pid":"b96a4ef52f9417983cf39f1c0fbb48cf668ff240","tid":1301894,"uid":207402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1f9cbeec80da733ee97f90c1b9c84f9bf4e8ab","tid":1301894,"uid":116734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"游行無人提無人推<br />\n光複上水集合地點換左北區運動場籃球場<br />\n有無人知？<br />\n開左tg group幫手搞口號 揾緊義工有無人知？<br />\n個個爭住講memo tvb<br />\n<br />\n我地游行要向政府 施壓 要求回應我哋五大訴求  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 是為主菜</span><br />\n<br />\n搞9 tvb同用memo紙 作另類文宣 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">是為配菜</span><br />\n<br />\ne+ 淨係搞tvb同memo紙大圍已經失焦 步緊雨傘後塵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"推 sor 都係啱啱先知改左地點"},{"pid":"a0d99df6091d51121f783143034825f0be828104","tid":1301894,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:28:00.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講\n我要見律師\n我唔解鎖電話\n我唔簽任何文件\n我要去醫院驗傷</code></pre>"},{"pid":"89c7305d5f620de83e643b4850c2bee5f72aef0d","tid":1301894,"uid":262662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42cffcf43b35185e6d28f0f0e85185bbbdc9b2e3","tid":1301894,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:26:40.000Z","msg":"文宣方面<br />\n首先要解釋下咩叫政治中立先<br />\n<br />\n就咁講警察違反政治中立唔係人人都明"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"文中有講過下：<br />\n<br />\n//《凌衞理報告書》：「所以，這個論據的重點是警務人員必須是沒有政治立場和中立的，而且必須讓公眾清楚可到這點。假若他們須和其他可自由決定是否認同某一政治立場的職工會一起，<span style=\"color: red;\">與政府舉行談判</span>，便不能做到上述的要求。」//<br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"color: red;\">警員沒有受過政治或公共政策的訓練，隨便發出政治聲明及參與外交更是越俎代庖</span>，違反公務員架構的紀律，屬嚴重失當。而警隊作為專業紀律部隊，更不應受到壓力就違反工作紀律，就像少爺兵一般，發晦氣撤崗。//"},{"pid":"16586b5e140c80258fee95116208c239e7431eab","tid":1301894,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b7d44b03de67540102d791d2350feccb6cf375","tid":1301894,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89c7305d5f620de83e643b4850c2bee5f72aef0d","tid":1301894,"uid":262662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42cffcf43b35185e6d28f0f0e85185bbbdc9b2e3","tid":1301894,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:26:40.000Z","msg":"文宣方面<br />\n首先要解釋下咩叫政治中立先<br />\n<br />\n就咁講警察違反政治中立唔係人人都明"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"文中有講過下：<br />\n<br />\n//《凌衞理報告書》：「所以，這個論據的重點是警務人員必須是沒有政治立場和中立的，而且必須讓公眾清楚可到這點。假若他們須和其他可自由決定是否認同某一政治立場的職工會一起，<span style=\"color: red;\">與政府舉行談判</span>，便不能做到上述的要求。」//<br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"color: red;\">警員沒有受過政治或公共政策的訓練，隨便發出政治聲明及參與外交更是越俎代庖</span>，違反公務員架構的紀律，屬嚴重失當。而警隊作為專業紀律部隊，更不應受到壓力就違反工作紀律，就像少爺兵一般，發晦氣撤崗。//"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫解釋左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拿你諗下班差佬每次鬧人都係比人鬧在先 包括英國<br />\n你要點樣清楚解釋連駁嘴都唔得先"},{"pid":"ac7f21c2c31acf04ab889aa76b1bf12800de4f4f","tid":1301894,"uid":29666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f6534e135ee84418fc7b21e77cf146ff0ea9f3","tid":1301894,"uid":262662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"譚文豪尋日講過差佬幾個協會不斷出聲鬧醫護人員、法律人員、議員甚至英國議員係完全違反《警隊條例》要求既政治中立，可以廢除獨立薪級表。好多人都唔明差佬點解紀律部隊中咁高人工，其實除左因為危險（消防唔危險咩？），仲因為有嚴格政治中立要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/121829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F121829&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=11290ecc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/121829</a><br />\n（作者Joe Yeung，文好長好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 節錄如下）<br />\n<br />\n//因為要豁免《警隊條例》中禁止參加職工會的限制，三個協會己獲得處長所承認，地位超然。可是員佐級協會當時仍屬法外之物，職級又不及前三者，所以修例就是要讓員佐級協會正名，將<span style=\"color: red;\">怨氣納入體制之中解決，亦透過升格與「大Sir」們睇齊，從而安撫情緒，收買人心</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n//香港警察隊員佐級協會就成為了高層與低級警員作溝通用的「既有渠道」，以溝通渠道換取警員守法，同時防止警員用任何方式向外洩憤，藉此確立警隊的紀律及專業操守的形象。而<span style=\"color: red;\">因為發生過警員圍攻廉署的失控暴力事件</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，員佐級協會的存在更是歷史上的一道明鏡，時刻提點警員任何原因都不是犯法的藉口，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">無論如何都不能用言語或行為對外發洩，協會的存在實在別具意義</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n//警員亦應明白，加入職工會並非毫無限制，他們只能對向內表達意見，亦只能討論<span style=\"color: red;\">薪酬待遇及福利事宜</span>，藉以保持政治中立及專業穩定的行為及形像。這是白紙黑字的立法原意，無可爭辯。<br />\n<br />\n政府一直保留這個限制，甚至於後來的薪酬檢討中亦可見一斑。1988年，政府繼續改革公務員薪酬待遇的制度，成立了「凌衞理委員會」，專門檢視紀律部隊的薪酬調整機制。<br />\n<br />\n當年重點之一，是警隊要求成立獨立的薪級表，<span style=\"color: red;\">使之與消防、海關、入境及懲教的薪酬調整機制拆開</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。當時《凌衞理報告書》回應了警隊的要求，時至今日，警隊的薪級仍是各隊之中最豐厚的一隊。而《凌衞理報告書》亦將消防隊伍由緊急紀律部隊降格為一般紀律部隊，更將警隊定性為「最終執法機關」（the agency of last resort）。如此一抬一踩地誇獎警隊，政府在警隊心理需求上實在是氹到盡，警隊理應知足及安份守己。//<br />\n<br />\n//給予警隊的豐厚薪酬及獨有超然地位，是因為《凌衞理報告書》充分考慮了警隊的工作性質（內有多段討論，有興趣可以詳讀），因而作出金錢上及心理上補償，確確實實是&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">they are well paid for it</span>&rdquo;。《凌衞理報告書》第8.44段明確寫出贊成警察擁有獨立薪酬機制的關鍵理據，主要是因為法例<span style=\"color: red;\">禁止警察參加工會、禁止擅離職守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及要求保持政治中立</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n文宣巴打請睇睇有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n[認真]文宣請入，要將焦點放係香港問題核心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301899\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301899</a></span>"},{"pid":"4ced5208688b1f7972773fb2307e162b8316ddb8","tid":1301894,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66d2bbf1c10e24f5acb798aedbfd5bf106e698b5","tid":1301894,"uid":35806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"我冇野講 <br />\n我要搵律師 (冇電話就問佢拎律師聯絡冊)<br />\n冇律師 我唔簽任何文件<br />\n我有權唔解鎖<br />\n我要食飯 飲水 拎毛氈 去廁所<br />\n我唔舒服想去醫院"},{"pid":"5c0cd942cdb029b29143ca30593d1f94f2762f12","tid":1301894,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔簽名"},{"pid":"da270dca1dff2cc369bf20229c891f344d77791b","tid":1301894,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b041b67f0b46ecaeb7be5552b028e73f55bd5872","tid":1301894,"uid":236710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"可以投訴。 有無巴打想send email.  可以留tg 傾下。"},{"pid":"1df31f8a432fe5a456a312f5eb59007068ee0e16","tid":1301894,"uid":88675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ab540d2bdae32326775c16d74ba48ab28b8052f","tid":1301894,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:45:27.000Z","msg":"有咩實際嘢可以發動到？取消個表得唔得？"}]}